#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Hunyuan-A13B-Instruct.md:1
msgid "Hunyuan-A13B-Instruct"
msgstr "Hunyuan-A13B-Instruct"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Hunyuan-A13B-Instruct.md:3
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "简介"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Hunyuan-A13B-Instruct.md:5
msgid ""
"Hunyuan-A13B-Instruct is a fine-grained hybrid expert model (MoE) "
"developed by Tencent. This model has a total of 80 billion parameters, 13"
" billion activation parameters, supports 256K ultra-long contexts, and "
"possesses native thought chain (CoT) reasoning capabilities."
msgstr ""
"Hunyuan-A13B-Instruct 是腾讯开发的细粒度混合专家模型（MoE）。该模型总参数量为800亿，激活参数量为130亿，支持256K超长上下文，并具备原生思维链（CoT）推理能力。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Hunyuan-A13B-Instruct.md:7
msgid "Environment Preparation"
msgstr "环境准备"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Hunyuan-A13B-Instruct.md:9
msgid "Model Weight"
msgstr "模型权重"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Hunyuan-A13B-Instruct.md:11
msgid ""
"`Hunyuan-A13B-Instruct`(BF16 version): [Download model "
"weight](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/Tencent-Hunyuan/Hunyuan-A13B-"
"Instruct)."
msgstr ""
"`Hunyuan-A13B-Instruct`（BF16版本）：[下载模型权重](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/Tencent-Hunyuan/Hunyuan-A13B-Instruct)。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Hunyuan-A13B-Instruct.md:13
msgid ""
"It is recommended to download the model weight to the shared directory of"
" multiple nodes, such as `/root/.cache/`"
msgstr "建议将模型权重下载到多节点的共享目录，例如 `/root/.cache/`"

