msgid "Key Performance Indicators"
msgstr "关键性能指标"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Hunyuan-A13B-Instruct.md:91
msgid "Based on verified CANN 8.5.1 test logs:"
msgstr "基于已验证的 CANN 8.5.1 测试日志："

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Hunyuan-A13B-Instruct.md:93
msgid ""
"Memory usage for weights: each NPU has a static memory usage of "
"approximately 37.46 GB."
msgstr "权重内存占用：每个 NPU 的静态内存占用约为 37.46 GB。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Hunyuan-A13B-Instruct.md:94
msgid ""
"Graph compilation (ACL Graph): with PIECEWISE mode enabled, the system "
"automatically captures the graph in approximately 18 seconds, which can "
"significantly accelerate subsequent inference."
msgstr "图编译（ACL Graph）：启用 PIECEWISE 模式后，系统大约在 18 秒内自动捕获图，这可以显著加速后续推理。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Hunyuan-A13B-Instruct.md:95
msgid ""
"KV cache capacity: the remaining NPU memory can provide concurrent cache "
"space for approximately 529,152 tokens."
msgstr "KV 缓存容量：剩余的 NPU 内存可为大约 529,152 个 token 提供并发缓存空间。"

