#, python-format
msgid ""
"On the GiteeAI platform, the model was tested and verified using the "
"AISBench tool on the GSM8K benchmark set: Under the 7cd45e version "
"configuration, the model achieved an accuracy of 94.77% in the accuracy "
"generation mode."
msgstr ""
"在 GiteeAI 平台上，使用 AISBench 工具在 GSM8K 基准集上对该模型进行了测试验证：在 7cd45e 版本配置下，该模型在精度生成模式下达到了 94.77% 的准确率。"

